{"tid":1397291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【I LOVE USA & TRUMP】你地班屌柒當撈侵嘅傻豬　到底明唔明咩叫撚狗？","createTime":"2019-08-02T11:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:22:04.000Z","uid":14328,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bcf26f6da6daf779c91a2cfa9d58bb9c78cd1b","tid":1397291,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"自當撈侵做左美國總統<br />\n每一次，美國對中國外交。<br />\n留意！係每一次！<br />\n<br />\n當撈侵對住習仔：「Come on! My best Friend Un GU GU 大家老友記，你呢排做得幾好喎！過嚟同我傾吓偈啦，搞掂個貿易戰佢～」<br />\n<br />\n習仔行到埋去，當撈侵啲o靚，美國國務院／Mike Pence 兜巴打落習主席面上，兜春袋踼鳩佢。<br />\n<br />\n習仔完全唔知乜撚野事，撳住自己春袋忍痛果陣。當撈侵又搭佢膊頭：Hey my friend! USA &amp; China will have a better future~ We gonna have a good deal right?!<br />\n<br />\n呢個套路，由貿易戰開打之前到而家，重複左１０次以上<br />\n點解仲有班豬兜唔撚明？<br />\n下下見到當撈侵話習仔做得唔錯就屌鳩侵<br />\n根本次次當撈侵幫中國講好說話嘅時候，就係佢郁鳩中國嘅時機。<br />\n點解咁耐都仲有人睇唔出？"},{"pid":"c00472d86b0492c19c1606899ff3d98f93876881","tid":1397291,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7e210e239f8d12f5c3ea6715eeb7e8ca27dc9f","tid":1397291,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edac27cb5d8b0e7f8867738ef63595102ec117d5","tid":1397291,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"邊個收到中國皮 我就support邊個<br />\n一日未收到一日都唔迷班政棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebb8c337e9720e3080cf53a7e2516a8496af30","tid":1397291,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}